org.glite.authz.common.http
Class JettyAdminServiceCLI

java.lang.Object
  org.glite.authz.common.http.JettyAdminServiceCLI

public class JettyAdminServiceCLI
extends Object

A command line tool used to communicate with JettyAdminService. Command line arguments are, in order:

  • hostname - hostname to which to connect
  • port - port to which to connect
  • command - admin command to execute
  • password - admin command password
